Name: LittleHTTPServer
Version: 0.1.2
Summary: Little bit extended SimpleHTTPServer
Home-page: http://bitbucket.org/t2y/littlehttpserver
Author: Tetsuya Morimoto
Author-email: tetsuya dot morimoto at gmail dot com
